Q: Rafael Núñez International Airport机场的三字码是什么？
SQL: SELECT iata_code FROM airport_fbo_details WHERE airport_name = "Rafael Núñez International Airport";
actual_SQL:
SELECT iata_code
FROM airport_fbo_details
WHERE airport_name = 'Rafael Núñez International Airport'
LIMIT 50;
